ygData.messageBody:
Thanks for the help people =)

I camped my bard in Rivervale and logged in with a low-level druid from
Kelethin that I play around with sometimes - checked the bard guild, and LO!
There she is! The spell-merchant selling lvl 8 and 15 songs was at her
normal post (second room of guildhall, on the left). I guess she WAS out
having a drink after all (or up on the roof?)...

Sartori D'Elsiraad
Bard of Kelethin of the 15th Chorus
Veeshan
